{"TopicId":131733,"ForumId":20,"TopicTitle":"[mod request] next launch window to planets/moons","CreatedByName":"kikill","CreatedById":130482,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-09T11:09:30Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"kikill","CreatedById":130482,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-09T11:09:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\na little window or HUD (like\u00A0KER) that shows the next launch window to planets or moons (a customizable list to only show Mars, Saturn, Titan...), so i don\u0027t miss my contracts deadline\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Evanitis","CreatedById":145424,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-09T11:14:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere\u0027s a \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/84005-10x-transfer-window-planner-v1400-dec-3/\u0022\u003ETransfer Window Planner\u003C/a\u003E addon with a nice porkchop plotter. MechJeb\u0027s advanced transfer function has the same.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOnce you get the date, you can just set up an alarm in KAC.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-02-09T11:14:49Z\u0022 title=\u002202/09/2016 11:14  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 9, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Evanitis\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Malah","CreatedById":96644,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-09T11:35:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can try Protractor : \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/75115-10x-protractor-continued-rendezvous-plugin-v251-may-15th-2015/\u0022\u003Ehttp://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/75115-10x-protractor-continued-rendezvous-plugin-v251-may-15th-2015/\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Tex_NL","CreatedById":58254,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-09T11:35:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222400565\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022131733\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221455016472\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022145424\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Evanitis\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n19 minutes ago, Evanitis said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere\u0027s a \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/84005-10x-transfer-window-planner-v1400-dec-3/\u0022\u003ETransfer Window Planner\u003C/a\u003E addon with a nice porkchop plotter. MechJeb\u0027s advanced transfer function has the same.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOnce you get the date, you can just set up an alarm in KAC.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you\u0027re going to use KAC why not simply use KAC\u0027s transfer window calculator? It might not have a porkchop plot but it is one less mod to worry about.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Streetwind","CreatedById":98962,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-09T14:45:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIndeed, KAC should be the tool of choice here. OP wants a small window that says hey, this planet is next. Which is literally what KAC does after you (manually) add the next handful of launch windows to the alarm list via the built-in function.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kikill","CreatedById":130482,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-09T15:56:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nthank you all, TAC indeed does the job \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ll try protractor too, i\u0027m curious\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}